        "latin_82": "Kalaa sayakfuruuna bi'ibaadatihim wayakuunuuna 'alaihim dhiddan",
        "latin_83": "Alam tara annaa arsalnaasy-syayaathiina 'alal kaafiriina ta'uzzuhum azzan",
        "latin_84": "Falaa ta'jal 'alaihim innamaa na'uddu lahum 'addan",
        "latin_85": "Yauma nahsyurul muttaqiina ilar-rahmani wafdan",
        "latin_86": "Wanasuuqul mujrimiina ila jahannama wirdan",
        "latin_87": "Laa yamlikuunasy-syafaa'ata ilaa maniittakhadza 'indar-rahmani 'ahdan",
        "latin_88": "Waqaaluuuut-takhadzar-rahmanu waladan",
        "latin_89": "Laqad ji-atum syai-an iddan",
        "latin_90": "Takaadus-samaawaatu yatafath-tharna minhu watansyaqqul ardhu watakhirrul jibaalu haddan",
        "latin_91": "An da'au lir-rahmani waladan",
        "latin_92": "Wamaa yanbaghii lir-rahmani an yattakhidza waladan",
        "latin_93": "In kullu man fiis-samaawaati wal ardhi ilaa aatiir-rahmani 'abdan",
        "latin_94": "Laqad ahshaahum wa'addahum 'addan",
        "latin_95": "Wakulluhum aatiihi yaumal qiyaamati fardan",
        "latin_96": "Innal-ladziina aamanuu wa'amiluush-shaalihaati sayaj'alu lahumur-rahmanu wuddan",
        "latin_97": "Fa-innamaa yassarnaahu bilisaanika litubasy-syira bihil muttaqiina watundzira bihi qauman luddan",
        "latin_98": "Wakam ahlaknaa qablahum min qarnin hal tuhissu minhum min ahadin au tasma'u lahum rikzan"
