        "latin_12": "Innii anaa rabbuka faakhla' na'laika innaka bil waadil muqaddasi thuwan",
        "latin_13": "Wa-anaaakhtartuka faastami' limaa yuuh(a)",
        "latin_14": "Innanii anaallahu laa ilaha ilaa anaa faa'budnii wa-aqimish-shalaata lidzikrii",
