        "latin_16": "Falaa yashuddannaka 'anhaa man laa yu'minu bihaa waattaba'a hawaahu fatard(a)",
        "latin_17": "Wamaa tilka biyamiinika yaa muus(a)",
        "latin_18": "Qaala hiya 'ashaaya atawakkau 'alaihaa wa-ahusyyu bihaa 'ala ghanamii waliya fiihaa maaaribu ukhr(a)",
        "latin_19": "Qaala alqihaa yaa muus(a)",
        "latin_20": "Fa-alqaahaa fa-idzaa hiya hai-yatun tas'(a)",
        "latin_21": "Qaala khudzhaa walaa takhaf sanu'iiduhaa siiratahaal aul(a)",
        "latin_22": "Waadhmum yadaka ila janaahika takhruj baidhaa-a min ghairi suu-in aayatan ukhr(a)",
        "latin_23": "Linuriyaka min aayaatinaal kubr(a)",
        "latin_24": "Adzhab ila fir'auna innahu thagh(a)",
        "latin_25": "Qaala rabbiisyrah lii shadrii",
