        "latin_62": "Wahuwal-ladzii ja'alallaila wannahaara khilfatan liman araada an yadz-dzakkara au araada syukuuran",
        "latin_63": "Wa'ibaadur-rahmanil-ladziina yamsyuuna 'alal ardhi haunan wa-idzaa khaathabahumul jaahiluuna qaaluuu salaaman",
