        "latin_70": "Walaa tahzan 'alaihim walaa takun fii dhaiqin mimmaa yamkuruun(a)",
        "latin_71": "Wayaquuluuna mata hadzaal wa'du in kuntum shaadiqiin(a)",
        "latin_72": "Qul 'asa an yakuuna radifa lakum ba'dhul-ladzii tasta'jiluun(a)",
