        "latin_75": "Wamaa min ghaa-ibatin fiissamaa-i wal ardhi ilaa fii kitaabin mubiinin",
        "latin_76": "Inna hadzaal quraana yaqush-shu 'ala banii israa-iila aktsaral-ladzii hum fiihi yakhtalifuun(a)",
        "latin_77": "Wa-innahu lahudan warahmatul(n)-lilmu'miniin(a)",
        "latin_78": "Inna rabbaka yaqdhii bainahum bihukmihi wahuwal 'aziizul 'aliim(u)",
        "latin_79": "Fatawakkal 'alallahi innaka 'alal haqqil mubiin(i)",
