        "latin_15": "Wa-in jaahadaaka 'al an tusyrika bii maa laisa laka bihi 'ilmun falaa tuthi'humaa washaahibhumaa fiiddunyaa ma'ruufan waattabi' sabiila man anaaba ilai-ya tsumma ilai-ya marji'ukum fa-unabbi-ukum bimaa kuntum ta'maluun(a)",
        "latin_16": "Yaa bunai-ya innahaa in taku mitsqaala habbatin min khardalin fatakun fii shakhratin au fiis-samaawaati au fiil ardhi ya'ti bihaallahu innallaha lathiifun khabiirun",
        "latin_17": "Yaa bunai-ya aqimish-shalaata wa'mur bil ma'ruufi waanha 'anil munkari waashbir 'ala maa ashaabaka inna dzalika min 'azmil amuur(i)",
        "latin_18": "Walaa tusha'iir khaddaka li-nnaasi walaa tamsyi fiil ardhi marahan innallaha laa yuhibbu kulla mukhtaalin fakhuurin",
        "latin_19": "Waaqshid fii masyyika waaghdhudh min shautika inna ankaral ashwaati lashautul hamiir(i)",
        "latin_20": "Alam tarau annallaha sakh-khara lakum maa fiis-samaawaati wamaa fiil ardhi wa-asbagha 'alaikum ni'amahu zhaahiratan wabaathinatan waminannaasi man yujaadilu fiillahi bighairi 'ilmin walaa hudan walaa kitaabin muniirin",
        "latin_21": "Wa-idzaa qiila lahumuuttabi'uu maa anzalallahu qaaluuu bal nattabi'u maa wajadnaa 'alaihi aabaa-anaa awalau kaanasy-syaithaanu yad'uuhum ila 'adzaabissa'iir(i)",
        "latin_22": "Waman yuslim wajhahu ilallahi wahuwa muhsinun faqadiistamsaka bil 'urwatil wutsqa wa-ilallahi 'aaqibatul amuur(i)",
        "latin_23": "Waman kafara falaa yahzunka kufruhu ilainaa marji'uhum fanunabbi-uhum bimaa 'amiluu innallaha 'aliimun bidzaatish-shuduur(i)",
        "latin_24": "Numatti'uhum qaliilaa tsumma nadhtharruhum ila 'adzaabin ghaliizhin",
        "latin_25": "Wala-in saaltahum man khalaqas-samaawaati wal ardha layaquulunnallahu qulil hamdu lillahi bal aktsaruhum laa ya'lamuun(a)",
        "latin_26": "Lillahi maa fiis-samaawaati wal ardhi innallaha huwal ghanii-yul hamiid(u)",
        "latin_27": "Walau annamaa fiil ardhi min syajaratin aqlaamun wal bahru yamudduhu min ba'dihi sab'atu abhurin maa nafidat kalimaatullahi innallaha 'aziizun hakiimun",
        "latin_28": "Maa khalqukum walaa ba' tsukum ilaa kanafsin waahidatin innallaha samii'un bashiirun",
        "latin_29": "Alam tara annallaha yuulijullaila fiinnahaari wayuulijunnahaara fiillaili wasakh-kharasy-syamsa wal qamara kullun yajrii ila ajalin musamman wa-annallaha bimaa ta'maluuna khabiirun",
