        "latin_32": "Wa-idzaa ghasyiyahum maujun kazh-zhulali da'awuullaha mukhlishiina lahuddiina falammaa najjaahum ilal barri faminhum muqtashidun wamaa yajhadu biaayaatinaa ilaa kullu khattaarin kafuurin",
