        "latin_23": "Uula-ikal-ladziina la'anahumullahu fa-ashammahum wa-a'ma abshaarahum",
        "latin_24": "Afalaa yatadabbaruunal quraana am 'ala quluubin aqfaaluhaa",
        "latin_25": "Innal-ladziina-artadduu 'ala adbaarihim min ba'di maa tabai-yana lahumul hudasy-syaithaanu sau-wala lahum wa-amla lahum",
        "latin_26": "Dzalika biannahum qaaluuu lil-ladziina karihuu maa nazzalallahu sanuthii'ukum fii ba'dhil amri wallahu ya'lamu israarahum",
        "latin_27": "Fakaifa idzaa tawaffathumul malaa-ikatu yadhribuuna wujuuhahum wa-adbaarahum",
        "latin_28": "Dzalika biannahumuuttaba'uu maa askhathallaha wakarihuu ridhwaanahu fa-ahbatha a'maalahum",
        "latin_29": "Am hasibal-ladziina fii quluubihim maradhun an lan yukhrijallahu adhghaanahum",
        "latin_30": "Walau nasyaa-u arainaakahum fala'araftahum bisiimaahum walata'rifannahum fii lahnil qauli wallahu ya'lamu a'maalakum",
        "latin_31": "Walanabluwannakum hatta na'lamal mujaahidiina minkum wash-shaabiriina wanabluwa akhbaarakum",
        "latin_32": "Innal-ladziina kafaruu washadduu 'an sabiilillahi wasyaaqquurrasuula min ba'di maa tabai-yana lahumul huda lan yadhurruullaha syai-an wasayuhbithu a'maalahum",
        "latin_33": "Yaa ai-yuhaal-ladziina aamanuu athii'uullaha wa-athii'uurrasuula walaa tubthiluu a'maalakum",
