        "latin_26": "Al-ladzii ja'ala ma'allahi ilahan aakhara fa-alqiyaahu fiil 'adzaabisy-syadiid(i)",
        "latin_27": "Qaala qariinuhu rabbanaa maa athghaituhu walakin kaana fii dhalalin ba'iidin",
        "latin_28": "Qaala laa takhtashimuu ladai-ya waqad qaddamtu ilaikum bil wa'iid(i)",
        "latin_29": "Maa yubaddalul qaulu ladai-ya wamaa anaa bizhalaamil(n)-lil'abiid(i)",
        "latin_30": "Yauma naquulu lijahannama haliimtal-ati wataquulu hal min maziidin",
        "latin_31": "Wa-uzlifatil jannatu lilmuttaqiina ghaira ba'iidin",
        "latin_32": "Hadzaa maa tuu'aduuna likulli au-waabin hafiizhin",
        "latin_33": "Man khasyiyar-rahmana bil ghaibi wajaa-a biqalbin muniibin",
