        "latin_7": "Idzaa ulquu fiihaa sami'uu lahaa syahiiqan wahiya tafuur(u)",
        "latin_8": "Takaadu tamai-yazu minal ghaizhi kullamaa ulqiya fiihaa faujun saalahum khazanatuhaa alam ya'tikum nadziirun",
