        "latin_10": "Waqaaluuu lau kunnaa nasma'u au na'qilu maa kunnaa fii ashhaabissa'iir(i)",
        "latin_11": "Faa'tarafuu bidzanbihim fasuhqan ashhaabissa'iir(i)",
        "latin_12": "Innal-ladziina yakhsyauna rabbahum bil ghaibi lahum maghfiratun wa-ajrun kabiirun",
        "latin_13": "Wa-asirruu qaulakum awiijharuu bihi innahu 'aliimun bidzaatish-shuduur(i)",
        "latin_14": "Alaa ya'lamu man khalaqa wahuwallathiiful khabiir(u)",
        "latin_15": "Huwal-ladzii ja'ala lakumul ardha dzaluulaa faamsyuu fii manaakibihaa wakuluu min rizqihi wa-ilaihinnusyuur(u)",
        "latin_16": "Aamintum man fiissamaa-i an yakhsifa bikumul ardha fa-idzaa hiya tamuur(u)",
