        "latin_26": "'Aalimul ghaibi falaa yuzhhiru 'ala ghaibihi ahadan",
        "latin_27": "Ilaa maniirtadha min rasuulin fa-innahu yasluku min baini yadaihi wamin khalfihi rashadan",
