        "latin_3": "Wa-idzaal bihaaru fujjirat",
        "latin_4": "Wa-idzaal qubuuru bu' tsirat",
        "latin_5": "'Alimat nafsun maa qaddamat wa-akh-kharat",
        "latin_6": "Yaa ai-yuhaa-insaanu maa gharraka birabbikal kariim(i)",
